first -> simple p2p network topology

second -> Wifi or LAN networking concept, CSMA and p2p network.
csma -> carrier sense multiple access -> p2p connected to bus and pass on packet.

netdevices -> modules use to communicate.
function send and rcv - params to set info : tx power per packet.

socket -> a pipe send rx based on some rules. Abstraction with API feature.
UDP and TCP sockets -> send a payload of data and then principles applied like header etc
